<seg id="1045">"& Povray; supports two methods of super-sampling. as standard is an adaptive, non-recursive method; adaptive because the super-sampling the neighbouring pixels with one. the second method is adaptive-recursive; recursive because each pixel is distributed over and over and adaptive because the recursion depth depends on the calculated color values."</seg>
